"Narrated 'Abdullah:\"I said: 'O Messenger of Allah (ﷺ)! What is the worst sin?' He said: 'That you make and equal to Allah, while it is He who created you.'\" He said: \"I said: 'Then what?' He said: 'That you kill your child fearing that he will eat with you.'\" He said: \"I said: 'Then what?' He said: 'That you commit adultery with your neighbors wife"